Linux Commands

Directory commands:

touch filename1                           = Create a file
touch filename2 filename3 filename4       = Create multiple files
touch -d "yyyy-mm-dd hh:mm:ss" filename   = Change file date & time
touch .filename                           = Create a hidden file
